show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://links.kukufm.com/uvrVxS
show.description: The troubled son of powerful MLA, is trapped beneath a legacy of emotional abuse and political expectations. But everything changes when he crosses paths with his mother, a fierce and self-made orphan from a foster home whose only family is her younger brother. Their connection sparks a series of confrontations — with class, love, identity, and the rotten roots of systemic power. As secrets unravel,  discovers her true lineage.
